<br>
I'm flat broke, and have nothing to show for 6 levels of experience than 19 water flasks, 19 rations, a Purity Belt, and a Tarnished Scythe.<br>
<br>
I'd like some advice from you more experienced players on where would be a good place to gain money, being an OE disciple of Innoruuk.  I've never been a DE before, so I'm unfamiliar with the general territory.  I'm of a mind to go to Innothule to kill frogloks so I can get some netted and cash, but they don't really drop that much.  I'm also tempted to visit the Warrens, except that I won't have anywhere to sell any loot (but at least I can get a nice looking weapon and sell molars for a plat or two each).  The paineel newbie area really is the nicest I've been in, as most decayed skeletons carry alot of copper if not silver, and alot of them are carrying rusty weapons that can be sharpened and sold to vendors for a couple gold.<br>
<br>
Any advice would be appreciated.  Thanks. <p>Shiden
<br>Dark Elf Shadowknight of Innoruuk
<br>Favored of the 4th Skull
<br>Firiona Vie
